description:
10 year old boys and girls have been mysteriously disappearing all around town. Rumor has it that a strange multicolored bus has also been seen driving around town at the same time, late at night. Are they connected? Are the rumors true? What is going on and what do the people in the bus want with all those children?

It's up to Sonic the hedgehog, siblings Sonia and Manic, and his boyfriend Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin to look into this and put a stop to whatever darkness it out there int he world right now.

replies.text:
Why would I roast AoStH and SATAM? They aren't modern sonic. Listen. Just because I think Modern Sonic is shit, it doesn't mean I have to hate on every little thing just because I can. I'm a very positive person and can see when things get something right. (sonic has black eyes and is fat in satam and aosth like sonic underground for example). But that doesn't mean I want to watch them either. Why? Because I don't feel like it bitch.
Why would I watch those shows when Sonic Underground is literally better in every single way? Characters like Bartleby, Manic, Sonia, Queen Aleena, Knuckles the Echidna, Sleet, Dingo and many more characters are not in those two shows so I don't have the care to watch them. If you want to watch those shows then go ahead. But they aren't cup of tea(or should I say plate of chili dogs, LOL). At the end of the day they don't hold a candle to good old SU
